OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,FA soldier from Plymouth says it is
OL,7,F"vital" the British Army improves its
OL,8,Funderstanding of complex reproductive
OL,9,Fhealth conditions, such as
OL,10,Fendometriosis and polycystic ovaries
OL,11,Fsyndrome (PCOS).
OL,13,FSince being diagnosed with
OL,14,Fendometriosis in 2019, Lance
OL,15,FBombardier Annie Robertson has
OL,16,Fsuffered six miscarriages and has
OL,17,Fundergone six extensive surgeries
OL,18,Fbecause of the conditions, and says
OL,19,Fher military career has been impacted
OL,20,Fas a result.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,FShe said: "My career has suffered with
OL,7,Fpromotions, I did get downgraded for a
OL,8,Fperiod of time because with all the
OL,9,Fmedication and hormone treatment, I
OL,10,Fwouldn't have been able to have been
OL,11,Fdeployed.
OL,13,F"So that did have an impact, and I
OL,14,Ffell quite behind with promotions.
OL,15,FWhich I am not resentful for, but it
OL,16,Fhas been hard, because I have worked
OL,17,Freally hard."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,FEndometriosis affects roughly 1 in
OL,7,Fevery ten women, making it the second
OL,8,Fmost common gynaecological condition
OL,9,Fin the UK.
OL,11,FIt is a condition where tissue,
OL,12,Fsimilar to the lining of a uterus,
OL,13,Fgrows in other places inside the body,
OL,14,Fsuch as on the ovaries or bowel. It
OL,15,Fcan cause severe inflammation, pain
OL,16,Fand scar tissue.
OL,18,FAs well as endometriosis, Annie also
OL,19,Fhas the complex reproductive
OL,20,Fconditions PCOS and adenomyosis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,FAnnie is based at the Royal Citadel in
OL,7,FPlymouth, and has told ITV News that
OL,8,Fshe faced "significant challenges" due
OL,9,Fto there being a limited understanding
OL,10,Fof these conditions in a male-
OL,11,Fdominated workforce.
OL,13,FAnnie has started delivering awareness
OL,14,Fworkshops and advocates for other
OL,15,Fservicewomen dealing with similar
OL,16,Fhealth issues.
OL,18,FReflecting on the response she has
OL,19,Freceived from fellow soldiers, Annie
OL,20,Fsaid: "It has been an eyeopener for
OL,21,Fthem, and educational."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,FStaff Sergeant Jodi Sitckland started
OL,7,Fgoing through the perimenopause in her
OL,8,Flate 30s. She said: "I was
OL,9,Fexperiencing hot flushes, muscle pain,
OL,10,Fbrain fog.
OL,12,F"It wasn't until I saw on the media,
OL,13,Fthanks to people like Davina McCall
OL,14,Fand shows like Loose Women, where they
OL,15,Fwere talking about the perimenopause -
OL,16,Fthat's when the penny dropped."
OL,18,FStaff Sergeant Stickland, in her role
OL,19,Fas a 'Menopause Champion', now
OL,20,Fdelivers awareness workshops across
OL,21,Fthe Armed Forces.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,FJodi said: "I really enjoy having the
OL,7,Frole and this platform, using my own
OL,8,Fexperience. Because I don't want any
OL,9,Fwoman to go through what I went
OL,10,Fthrough - the uncertainty of not
OL,11,Fknowing.
OL,13,F"The presentation is aimed at all
OL,14,Fgenders and ranks. I can educate women
OL,15,Fso they can be prepared for when it
OL,16,Feventually happens.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,F"And for men as well, because being in
OL,7,Fa male-dominated environment, they
OL,8,Fneed to know just as much. They won't
OL,9,Fbe going through it, but indirectly,
OL,10,Fthis is going to affect them."
OL,12,FJodi says that a few years ago, a
OL,13,Fmenopause study was carried out with a
OL,14,Fcross-section of servicewomen.
OL,16,FIt found found 80% considered to
OL,17,Feither be peri or post-menopause and
OL,18,Fnearly 30% were thinking of leaving
OL,19,Fthe Armed Forces because of the
OL,20,Fsymptoms.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,FA British Army spokesperson has told
OL,7,FITV News: "We are immensely proud of
OL,8,Fthe contribution female service people
OL,9,Fmake to Army life. We provide a
OL,10,Fvariety of support mechanisms,
OL,11,Fincluding specific policies and
OL,12,Fdedicated information resources
OL,13,Frelating to women's health.
OL,15,F"We are committed to normalising
OL,16,Fdiscussions about women's health
OL,17,Ftopics and encouraging greater
OL,18,Funderstanding among all personnel.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,F"The advice we provide to servicewomen
OL,7,Fconsiders the nature of their job and
OL,8,Fthe unique environments they work in.
OL,10,F"For this reason, if a servicewoman
OL,11,Fexperiences any health problem she
OL,12,Fwill be provided care by specialised
OL,13,Fmilitary medical consultants with a
OL,14,Fdeep understanding of the unique
OL,15,Fnature of military life."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783678767
OL,3,CSoldier battling endometriosis calls
OL,4,Cfor better support within Army
OL,6,FThe Army spokesperson added that they
OL,7,Fcontinue to work closely with
OL,8,Fpersonnel including with the
OL,9,Fdevelopment of the Servicewomen's
OL,10,FHealth Improvement Focus Team which
OL,11,Fhas been created to improve service
OL,12,Flife for female soldiers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
